Collect uncommon ore found within Stangraf for Quickbeam.
'These are some interesting ore samples! Please try to found any more of this and return it to me so I can learn more of its properties.'

Stangraf has long been a source of iron and other metals commonly used for weapons, armour, and construction. Occasionally this mine has uncovered rarer veins, and it appears the new residents have uncovered a few. Perhaps Quickbeam would have some use for it.
'This is some unusual ore! I have never seen this type of ore before, but have read about it's discovery ages ago. You have done well to find it and return these samples to me.'
Uncommon ore can sometimes be found in the Stangraf.\n\nYou should collect uncommon ore and bring it to Elfward.
